org.ensor.algorithms.astar
This is an abstract implementation of the classic AStar algorithm.
org.ensor.algorithms.astar.grid
This package contains an implementation of a square and hex map suitable for use in the A-Star algorithm.

org.ensor.algorithms.cubicspline
This package contains code for cubic splines and other techniques for calculating a smooth path between a set of points.

This package contains a generic topological sort algorithm.
org.ensor.data.atom
This package holds objects which represent abstract data which can be serialized.
org.ensor.data.atom.json
This package contains serializers to convert the Dictionary and List structures into JSON and back again.
org.ensor.data.atom.log
This package contains utility classes to help with logging of the Atom, Dictionary, and List structures.
org.ensor.data.atom.xml
This package contains a serialzier for writing the dictionary and list objects to XML documents and reading them back again.

This package contains 3d geometrical constructs such as vectors, rotation matrices, etc.

This package contains a TTY object which can be used by various motor and sensor controllers.
